      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to the rotating-frame Navier-Stokes solver; observed order of accuracy 1.97 (expected 2nd order). Benchmark lid-driven cavity and Taylor-Couette results match published reference data within 0.5%. Meets Gradation 2."
