      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation performed on three systematically refined meshes (2.1 M, 5.8 M, 14.3 M cells). GCI on the relative hemolysis index at the worst-case operating point is 8.3% on the medium grid and 6.1% on the fine grid — marginally above the 5% threshold. Discretization uncertainty is documented but the fine-grid GCI does not satisfy the Gradation 2 acceptance criterion. Assessed at Gradation 1."
