      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index predicted vs. measured across 5 operating points; mean absolute error 7.2%, maximum 11.4%. Normalized index of agreement 0.91. Systematic over-prediction at high-speed low-flow corrected by turbulent viscosity scaling. Meets Gradation 2 output comparison requirements."
